# Production environment template

Copy to your secret manager or server env (never commit filled values).

```bash
# Required
DATABASE_URL=postgresql+asyncpg://USER:PASSWORD@HOST:5432/airtasker
SECRET_KEY=replace-with-64-char-random-string

# Environment
ENVIRONMENT=production
CORS_ALLOWED_ORIGINS=https://app.yourdomain.com

# AI (production)
USE_MOCK_CHATBOT=false
GEMINI_API_KEY=
USE_PINECONE_RAG=false

# Payments (production Razorpay live keys)
RAZORPAY_KEY_ID=
RAZORPAY_KEY_SECRET=
RAZORPAY_PAYOUT_ACCOUNT_NUMBER=
RAZORPAY_WEBHOOK_SECRET=

# KYC
KYC_PROVIDER=stub
KYC_REQUIRED_FOR_PAYOUT=true
KYC_WEBHOOK_SECRET=

# Beta scope (adjust when expanding launch)
BETA_MODE_ENABLED=true
BETA_CATEGORIES=electrical,plumbing,cleaning
BETA_PIN_CODES=248001,110001,560001
BETA_LANGUAGES=en,hi,ta

# Feature flags
FEATURE_FLAG_AI_CHAT=true
FEATURE_FLAG_VOICE_INPUT=true
FEATURE_FLAG_KYC_PAYOUT=true
FEATURE_FLAG_RAZORPAY_CHECKOUT=true
FEATURE_FLAG_DISPUTES=true

# Ops
ENABLE_PROMETHEUS_METRICS=true
REDIS_URL=
```

Deploy:

```bash
docker compose -f docker-compose.yml -f docker-compose.prod.yml up --build -d
python scripts/smoke_deploy.py https://api.yourdomain.com
python scripts/go_live_watch.py --base-url https://api.yourdomain.com --minutes 60
```
